modName: Allocs Web and Map Rendering Dwarfmaster Flavour

modDescription:
This is Dwarfmaster1974’s first mod, which came to live after he presented his own [map](http://der-heimat-hafen.de/) in between a ‘7 Days to Die’ discussion on Discord.

So please be nice to him, he is just a newbie on that.

Please have a look at the [README.md](https://github.com/OmitLeChuck/7D2D_Allocs_WebAndMapRendering_dwarfmaster_flavour#readme) for an overview of the features and configuration.

**[Download](https://github.com/OmitLeChuck/7D2D_Allocs_WebAndMapRendering_dwarfmaster_flavour/archive/refs/heads/main.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/27659-allocs-webandmaprendering-dwarfmaster-flavour/).
